Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.47,0:01:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能好兴奋  烤架上面煎肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon I will get a thrill, cooking patties on my grill
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:13.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,288)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,292)}蟹堡王因海胆暂停营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(238,474)}入口
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.95,0:01:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王因海胆暂停营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Krusty Krab closed on account of urchins"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(390,934)}往门缝塞钱随意\N谢谢合作   蟹老板
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.20,0:01:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是在做噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must be in a nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是噩梦  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no nightmare, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王要暂停营业一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm closing the old girl up for a week
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把海胆除干净
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get rid of those prickly pests
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我有灭海胆公司的优惠券
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plus, I had a coupon for Urchin B-Gone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What will become of me?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.50,0:01:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整个星期得干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do for a whole week?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别急  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow your roll, Boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.22,0:01:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把你租给别人家的店上一星期的班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've rented you out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to a different establishment for the week
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.35,0:01:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样这一周就还能有收入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so is not to disrupt me incomin' monies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打临时工一听就很刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A temporary job sounds so adventurous
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥也一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Squidward coming too?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不来  我让他去搞文娱业了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, I got him a job in the entertainment industry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总比跟海绵宝宝上班强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still better than working with SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.59,0:02:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去哪上班  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where will I be working, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要在强人俱乐部这边上班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be working right here at The Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:09.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1184,218)}强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.49,0:02:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太强人的地方我遭不住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That place is too tough for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班用不着当强人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be tough to work here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着像强人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just gotta look tough
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.79,0:02:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你样子就像个强人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you look like a tough guy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉不强  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't feel tough, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now when you go in there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就走到最大的客人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go up to the biggest customer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正视他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look him squarely in the eye
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他知道你对人家的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And let him know exactly what you think of him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.33,0:02:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最会正视了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm great at looking squarely
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别搞笑了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No funny business, Boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.15,0:03:19.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向你说出我对你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:19.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell you exactly what I think of you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的浅蓝眼睛最漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have got the most beautiful baby blue eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从我妈那儿遗传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got 'em from me mother
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blue eyes?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,众所周知我绿眼睛才最漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows my green eyes are the most beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.92,0:03:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to The Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是这里的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the owner of this joint
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表示你现在要给我干活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That means youse works for me now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的新老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My new boss
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.74,0:03:56.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:56.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So nice to meet--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤架在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the spatoola
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点把吃的做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now make with the grub
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just out of curiosity
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家上一任厨师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what happened to your last fry cook?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我们每月最佳员工墙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's our employee of the month wall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,972)}每月最佳员工
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.35,0:04:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好好干活  下一张照片就挂你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your photo is gonna be next if you don't get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别怕  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟在蟹堡王工作差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll be just like working at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡多做点哦  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep those patties comin', pal
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份撒满钉子的砖块  多加机油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme a brick covered in nails with extra motor oil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(824,924)}芝 麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1026,924)}贝 果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:38.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1362,924)}糖 浆
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this garbage?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要的是撒满钉子的砖块
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I asked for a brick covered with nails
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为是点餐黑话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought that was just diner lingo
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撒满钉子的砖块  多加机油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brick covered with nails, extra motor oil
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很有强人俱乐部的范
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salty Spitoon style
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这三明治就是强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's a tough sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.53,0:05:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,砖块好嫩  钉子烤得好熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The brick is so tender, and the nails are roasted
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.94,0:05:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有好几单要做  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got some more orders for you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,72份撒满机油的砖块马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,72 bricks covered in motor oil coming right up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya know?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙有什么意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya say, gang?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是火爆泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Puff the Tuff
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火爆泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puff the Tuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:38.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(992,588)}胖冬瓜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.12,0:05:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份脏玻璃杯包碎玻璃高脚杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme a tall glass of broken glass in a dirty glass
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能是他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It can't be him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁点了炸弹烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who ordered the bomb-becue?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位是泡芙老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么火爆泡芙会怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is Puff the Tuff afraid of you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她可能没认出我现在是个强人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She probably didn't recognize me now that I'm a tough guy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞋带松了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My shoelace is untied
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Safety first
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新来的那个小厨子还挺强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That new little cook seems pretty tough
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看他有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see how tough he is
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.34,0:06:33.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强人大考验开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:33.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the trials of toughness begin
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机械海公牛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mechanical Sea-bull
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor thing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人老是骑你  估计让你特别烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're probably tired of people riding you all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息一下  骑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a break and ride me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打水泥袋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Punching bag
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打得好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice punch, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,体毛力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Body hair strength
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用下我黑心面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just use my abrasive side
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.70,0:07:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布强人俱乐部里最强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I declare the toughest guy at The Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为我们的强人领导
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As our tough guy leader
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.32,0:07:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有资格可以做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have the power to do whatever you want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1392,540)}强人章程
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.26,0:07:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的话  我想给这里来点狂野的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, I've got a few wild ideas for this place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}一天后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:11.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1068,264)}强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.80,0:08:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备进裤头村最强人的地方打群架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to rumble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the toughest place in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:40.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1456,208)}强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:40.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(206,368)}儿童乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the right place
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.77,0:08:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找这里的老板谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I demand to speak to whoever's in charge
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么来谈话的是个奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is the cheese talking to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是要找强人领导谈话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You asked to speak with the tough leader?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, really
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁让这家伙进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who let this guy in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你对全新室内装饰赞赏有加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you're admiring the new décor
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快告诉他装饰得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell him how it is, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上再做个更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do him one better
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家前来弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come one and come all to The Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1334,274)}弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有不少杯子蛋糕还有气球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where all of our cupcakes come with a balloon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果亲亲抱抱是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you like head kisses and cuddly hugs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就举起牛奶  装进爱妈妈杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And raise up your milk with "I heart Mom" mugs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1580,698)}我爱妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.32,0:09:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.05,0:09:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们表现得跟弱小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're acting like a bunch of weenies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:45.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1128,924)}香 肠
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weenies?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有的是  大家抢着要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have those, and they are to die for
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.17,0:09:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要加点新鲜腌料增添风味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dab of freshly pickled relish, perhaps?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要哭就别来弱人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There ain't no cryin' in The Softy--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说强人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean The Salty Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就这样了  毛毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there is now, buttercup
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不喜欢就给我走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if you don't like it, you can hike it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.75,0:10:18.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看海绵宝宝什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:18.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see how SpongeBob is doing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This oughta be good
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹  你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs, what are you doin' here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一周时间还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The week ain't up yet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝没给你们惹麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob isn't giving you a problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  他是这里的舞会女王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, he's the belle of the ball
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  客人都特别喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, the customers like him so much
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要永远把他留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna keep him on permanently
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.82,0:10:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在就得跟我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's coming back with me right now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来带你回去  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better take you home, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方太强  你遭不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is much too tough for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可能会受伤的  知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You might get hurt, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fare thee well, you old Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会永远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll always have
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙绑走了我们领导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy is kidnapping our leader
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy Spitoon
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弱人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Softy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spitoon
