Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772,784)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.55,0:11:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把12件换洗内裤装你行李箱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I managed to fit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,12 changes of underwear in your suitcase
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装这么多外出够用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will that be enough for the trip?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要外出三天时间  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be gone for three days, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  可以够用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so yeah, that should cover it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸要去贝壳城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy has to go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.85,0:12:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,参加一年一度的末日装备博览会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the annual Doomsday Device Expo in Shell City
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你找个终极邪恶道具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's gonna find you an instrument of ultimate evil
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会好好找的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给老妈留了不少说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I left lots of instructions for Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.32,0:12:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让她知道我外出的时候要怎么照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so she knows exactly how to care for you while I'm gone
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小家伙需要不少爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wittle man just needs wots of extra wove
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是有什么三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I would destroy the whole world
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要毁灭全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if anything happened to him
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.81,0:12:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你出租船到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your taxi's here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(870,272)}出租船
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Off you go, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Spotty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice trip
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只剩下你和我了  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's just you and me, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton's instructions
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点  坏变形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot, bad amoeba
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板的小说明哪里用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs Plankton's little notes?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这精密的AI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sophisticated AI like myself
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照顾简简单单的有机生物可不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should have no problem with a simple organic being
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要来点基本的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All he needs is a basic analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,378)}分析中
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还没把你分析完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not done analyzing you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578,292)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heel, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.97,0:13:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点本来就该这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能充点气就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he needs a little pumping up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我害点点死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I killed him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁让你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who sent you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然要来这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗要跟点点玩一阵子  记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary has a playdate with Spot, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟点点玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With Spot, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, the thing is
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点今天玩不了  因为点点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot can't play today because he's, uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.49,0:14:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,busy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点特别忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's busy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.18,0:14:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忙着要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,busy being, um
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碎成渣还溅得到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All over the place in bits and pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我害点点炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I exploded him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's Spot all right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点  过来海绵宝宝这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot, come to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么修复好点点的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you figure that out?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点跟小蜗玩都会这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This happens all the time when he plays with Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.54,0:15:07.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认  在痞老板外出期间照顾点点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:07.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I admit, looking after Spot while Plankton is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我想的还要难搞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is proving trickier than I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点大概得来消耗一点能量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he needs to burn off some energy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么会这么壮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you so strong?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点  看你捣的乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot, look at this mess
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不想跟小蜗一样乖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to be a good boy like Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子上的应该不是我的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I nose this ain't my donut
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点跑太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's too fast
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况还能糟到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can this get any worse?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是凯伦的脑袋  请问你要找谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen's head, how may I direct your call?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.77,0:16:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以找凯伦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I talk to Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.67,0:16:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在发声音  现在我要来问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Throwing my voice, and now it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,末日博览会怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's the Doomsday Expo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:54.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,524)}末日装备博览会
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圆满结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's over
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要早早回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming home early
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.05,0:16:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're what?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I bought
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能找到的最邪恶的统治世界装备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the most evil world-conquering device I could find
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总之点点现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how's my little Spot?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让点点接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put him on the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想念点点的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I miss his voice
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让点点接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put Spot on the phone?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This phone?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小家伙还在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's my wittle man
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一听就知道老妈对你呵护有加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like Mommy is taking good care of you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个白痴把这个小行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some idiot left this tiny suitcase
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,落在明火旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next to an open flame
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁痞老板还没回来  赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get back before Plankton comes home
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.73,0:17:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How was your shift?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你海霸糊碰都没碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't touched your chum
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不吃海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't really eat chum
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, me neither
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.77,0:18:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喂点点了没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you fed Spot yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  点点不会从电池消耗能量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, does he not consume power from his battery?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.12,0:18:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点要消耗别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He consumes other stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you still hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.27,0:18:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  要不要来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, how 'bout a nice, um
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸巾盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a napkin dispenser?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.94,0:18:41.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点居然什么都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:41.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot'll eat anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}一顿大餐之后
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再吃了  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就快把咱家都吃穷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You literally just ate us out of house and home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你还饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, you're still hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要的所有食物我全都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you all the nourishment you'll ever need
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  我合成了永久营养药丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, I synthesized a perpetual nutrient pill
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以不停把你喂饱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll keep feeding you so you'll be full
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点长大算是正常现象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he supposed to be getting bigger?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种情况我没计算过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was not in my calculations
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会儿会不长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gonna stop soon?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让药丸效力停止的程序我没写
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't program the pill to stop
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得多加小心对待你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta be careful with you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要做错一步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One wrong move
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就会把整座海洋全炸飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll blow the whole ocean sky-high
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光不长久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The good times never last
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.44,0:20:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我便签没写要让点点变大的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,None of my sticky notes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,said to turn Spot into a behemoth
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来不会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this wouldn't have happened
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.40,0:20:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不是你没把点点训练好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you had trained him properly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a busy man
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就该按我的说明来做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should've been following my instructions
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.75,0:20:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是你的电脑老婆  不是电脑女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am your computer wife, not your computer maid
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.85,0:20:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,键盘整天让人敲  还得做牛做马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I slave all day over a hot keyboard--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以都是我的错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So everything is my fault
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对于你  一切都是一和零
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all ones and zeroes with you, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怕是你故意要让点点比我还要大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You probably made Spot bigger than me on purpose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我觉得自己很渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To make me feel small
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你全身就属你嘴巴最大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your mouth is the biggest part of you--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有跟你有关的东西都特小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything about you is small
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.81,0:20:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的心胸特宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My heart is big
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不应该将就着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:57.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should not have settled
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像要分裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think he's dividing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点点不喜欢看老爸老妈吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't like it when Mommy and Daddy fight
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来老爸这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to Papa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来爸爸这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.37,0:21:12.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点
